      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babyed this car since day one, and it's in absolutely flawless condition inside and out. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it! \u2728",
