    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. The engine's induction is handled via eight individual throttle bodies, providing telepathic throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This example is mechanically pristine, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already completed. The chassis remains incredibly taut, benefiting from the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system which maintains perfect damping characteristics. Finished in Alpine White with a carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity, this vehicle exhibits factory-level torsional rigidity and flawless cosmetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Original paint. New tires. Interior flawless.",
      "price": 43500.0,
