      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with zero imperfections, as it has been climate-control garage-kept since day one. Inside, the premium leather seats remain firm and unscuffed, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the panoramic sunroof, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history and incredibly low mileage. The engine bay is pristine, and the ride quality is as smooth and quiet as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
